des:
You can simply ask Alexa to control your Savvi Security system. After connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
(1) Download our "Savvi Security" app in app market then register an account;
(2) Configure our devices in our "Savvi Security" app and change the appropriate name for your devices;
(3) Enable "Savvi Security" skill, and you'll be navigated to "Savvi Security" login page;
(4) Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(5) Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
Alexa, turn on the porch light.
Alexa, turn off the porch light.
Alexa, turn on plug.
Alexa, turn off plug.
